      "default": "To keep your jewelry sparkling, clean it gently with a soft cloth and mild soap. Avoid harsh chemicals and store pieces separately in a jewelry box. Remove jewelry before swimming, exercising, or sleeping to prevent damage."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
